'''法爾茅斯大學'''（{{lang-en|Falmouth University}}，{{lang-kw|Pennskol Aberfala}}）是一所位於[[英國|英國]][[康沃爾郡|康沃爾郡]][[法爾茅斯_(康沃爾郡)|法爾茅斯]]和[[彭林_(康沃爾郡)|彭林]]的藝術大學，歷史可追溯至1902年，2005年3月獲得頒發學位許可，<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.falmouth.ac.uk/index.php?option=com_content&task=category&sectionid=8&id=50&Itemid=138 |title=Combined Universities in Cornwall |publisher=University College Falmouth |accessdate=2008-03-19 |archive-date=2018-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618031144/https://www.falmouth.ac.uk/index.php?option=com_content&task=category&sectionid=8&id=50&Itemid=138 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2008年4月與[[達林頓藝術學院|達林頓藝術學院]]合併。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.falmouth.ac.uk/138/the-college-8/dartington%27s-merger-with-ucf-206.html |title=Merger with Dartington College of Arts |publisher=University College Falmouth |accessdate=2008-09-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080914074542/http://www.falmouth.ac.uk/138/the-college-8/dartington%27s-merger-with-ucf-206.html |archivedate=2008-09-14 }}</ref> 2012年12月9日獲大學資格。<ref>{{cite web|title=Falmouth University status officially confirmed|url=http://www.falmouth.ac.uk/151/news-from-university-college-falmouth-5/media-releases-47/falmouth-university-status-officially-confirmed-5157.html|publisher=Falmouth University|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130116175355/http://www.falmouth.ac.uk/151/news-from-university-college-falmouth-5/media-releases-47/falmouth-university-status-officially-confirmed-5157.html|archivedate=2013-01-16}}</ref>

